title: The 'Yellowjackets' Penultimate Episode
description:
Bill Simmons, Chris Ryan, and Joanna Robinson break down the penultimate episode of 'Yellowjackets' Season 1. They give some theories for the episode, talk about some of their favorite moments from the season, and make some predictions for the finale.

Hosts: Bill Simmons, Chris Ryan, and Joanna Robinson
Producer: Kaya McMullen
